---
title: Quick Sausage Bolognese over Spaghetti
description: From Italian trattorias to the ordinary American kitchen, spaghetti with tomato sauce is one of those timeless dishes that has a place on virtually every dinner table. But how do you keep a recipe that’s so well-worn exciting? You fill it up with flavorful ingredients. In our version, Italian sausage, mushrooms, and spinach are brought in to add an umami-packed boost and make the sauce rich, thick, and hearty. It’s comfortingly classic without being boring.
